 </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, le maître de cavalerie <supplied reason="lost">Untel</supplied> fils de Philytas, les gymnasiarques <supplied reason="lost">Untel</supplied> 
                (5) fils de Theod<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <supplied reason="lost">Untel</supplied> fils de Lysis, <supplied reason="lost">Untel</supplied> fils d'Etéarkhos,
                ainsi que celui des seniors <supplied reason="lost">Untel</supplied> fils d'Anaxa<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, (10) les <foreign rend="italic">triakatioi</foreign>:
                Kallias fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>,</p>
                <p>a) <note>une colonne de noms et patronymes</note>,</p>
                <p>b) (22) Hérakleidas fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, Hérakleitos fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, Theudôros fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, Theudôros fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, Theudôros fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, Theudotos fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>an fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>,
                <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>ès fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, (30) <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>n fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, the master of riding <supplied reason="lost">so-and-so</supplied> son of Philytas, the gymnasiarchs <supplied reason="lost">So-and-so</supplied> 
                (5) son of Theod<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <supplied reason="lost">So-and-so</supplied> son of Lysis, <supplied reason="lost">So-and-so</supplied> son of Etearchos,
