                <p>a) <note>one column of names and fathers' names</note>,</p>
                <p>b) (22) Herakleidas son of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, Herakleitos son of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, Theudoros son of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, Theudoros son of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, Theudoros son of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, Theudotos son of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>an son of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>,
